\begin_layout Itemize

\size scriptsize
Business intelligence and analytics 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "kouper2021challenges"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Note Note
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Companies gather data from different sources (sales, customer interaction,
 marketing campaigns, etc.) and centralize it within data warehouses.
 Data exchange protocols make building and updating these warehouses efficient.
 This combined data fuels powerful analytics tools to get insights that
 drive business strategy.
\end_layout

\end_inset

 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\size scriptsize
Finance and banking 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Elsaify2021Data"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Note Note
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Credit checks, risk assessment, and fraud detection rely heavily on data
 exchange.
 Financial institutions securely exchange information across multiple systems
 to assess the creditworthiness of individuals or to flag suspicious transaction
s.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

