\begin_layout Plain Layout
Data exchanges often operate as marketplaces where companies can buy or
 sell user data.
 This data often includes demographics, browsing behavior, interests, and
 more.
 Marketers use this data to fine-tune targeted advertising and create highly
 personalized campaigns.
\end_layout

\end_inset


