\begin_layout FrameSubtitle
The Growth of Data Centers in Colombia
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Latin America's technological revolution plays a crucial role in promoting
 
\series bold
regional economic growth
\series default
, closing the digital gap, creating a foundation for improved connectivity,
 innovation, and robust digital infrastructure 
